<div class="charts_jumbo" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
      <h1 class="cabin" style="color: #FFF;">Chart it out.</h1>
      <h3 class="cabin" style="color: #00897B;">Insights into how brands are using Snapchat.</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container" style="background-color: #FFF;">
	<h4 class="cabin" style="letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: -3px;">DISTRIBUTION OF STORIES BY DAY OF WEEK</h3>
	<small><i>Trailing 14 Days</i></small>
	<%= image_tag "weekdist.png", :class => "img-responsive" %>
	This chart demonstrates <b>which days are the most popular</b> for brands to post Stories on Snapchat.
	<br /><br />
	The calculation is performed gathering data over the most recent 14 day period and using the formula: (Stories during a specific day of the week) &divide; (total Stories during 14 day period).
</div>
<br /><br />
<div class="container" style="background-color: #FFF;">
	<h4 class="cabin" style="letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: -3px;">AVERAGE ACTIVITY BY INDUSTRY</h3>
	<small><i>
		Trailing 14 Days
	</i></small>
	<%= image_tag "industact.png", :class => "img-responsive" %>
	This chart demonstrates which industries are <b>most active</b> with Stories on Snapchat.
	<br /><br />
	The calculation is performed gathering data over the most recent 14 day period and using the formula: (total number of active days by brands per industry) &divide; (total number of active brands by industry).
</div>
<br /><br />
<div class="container" style="background-color: #FFF;">
	<h4 class="cabin" style="letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: -3px;">BRAND ACTIVITY</h3>
	<small><i>
		Trailing 14 Days
	</i></small>
	<%= image_tag "numberact.png", :class => "img-responsive" %>
	This chart demonstrates <b>how often</b> brands share Stories brands on Snapchat.
</div>